Description: Marvis Frazier: An 11-part series focusing on previously unseen
footage of Mike Tyson's first 25 pro fights. 

Tyson takes on Joe Frazier's son Marvis.



Please help your fellow pirates by seeding after download!

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

And let me just say it's been a pleasure to share Mike Tyson's earliest fights with you all when he truly was raw and uncut and ready to take on the world with strength, skill and aggression in the ring we'd never seen before, or have witnessed since. 

I hope you all enjoyed the series as much as I did watching him destroy all in his path, giving us a glimpse of what was yet to come, and what even more could have been.....

We should all feel priviliged to have witnessed a boxer like him in the ring because we're unlikely to see anything similar in our lifetimes again. Thanks for the memories Iron Mike. /akhiugo
